---
title: "invalidateOrders (GPV2CompatibleAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_role: caller has ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_iter: role verified
    q_iter --> q_invalidate: i < orderUids.length
    q_invalidate --> q_iter: i_gpV2Settlement.invalidateOrder(orderUids[i]); i++
    q_iter --> [*]: i >= orderUids.length

    note right of q_iter
        INV-001: Only ORDER_MANAGER_ROLE can invalidate orders
        INV-002: All orderUids are forwarded to GPv2Settlement for invalidation
        INV-003: After invalidation, settlement contract will reject these order UIDs
    end note
